<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Memoria - Todo App</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #333333;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        
        .feature {
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

            .feature h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .feature p {
                font-size: 16px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .feature img {
                width: 200px;
                height: 200px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

        .colorful-text {
            color: blue; /* Replace with your desired color */
        }

        .emphasized-text {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to <span class="colorful-text">Memoria!</span></h1>
        <img src="~/images/notas.png" style="width:100px;height:100px;" />

        <div class="feature">
            <h2 class="emphasized-text">Note Taking</h2>
            <p>Effortlessly capture your thoughts, ideas, and important information. Take notes in a clean and intuitive interface, allowing you to focus on your content.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Adding Reminders</h2>
            <p>Stay organized by setting reminders for important tasks and deadlines. Never miss a deadline again with customizable reminders that help you stay on top of your commitments.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
            <h2 class="emphasized-text">Collaborative Writing</h2>
            <p>Work together with your team or friends in real-time to create and edit notes. Collaborate effortlessly by inviting others to contribute and edit your notes, making it easy to collaborate on projects or share information.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Sharing the Note</h2>
            <p>Easily share your notes with others via email, social media, or direct links. Share your valuable information with others.</p>
        </div>

        <a asp-controller="Accounts" asp-action="Register" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Get Started</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>

<script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
